
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pre-Visit Intake Form - MyChart | Kaiser Permanente</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: #f5f7fa;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .header {
            background: #0066cc;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }

        .header-content {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo-section {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }

        .kp-logo {
            background: white;
            color: #0066cc;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .mychart-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .patient-info {
            text-align: right;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .breadcrumb {
            background: #004499;
            padding: 10px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .breadcrumb-content {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
            color: white;
        }

        .breadcrumb a {
            color: #b3d9ff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .breadcrumb a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 30px 20px;
        }

        .form-header {
            background: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
            border: 1px solid #e1e8ed;
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .form-title {
            color: #0066cc;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .form-subtitle {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .epic-badge {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .survey-form {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
            border: 1px solid #e1e8ed;
            border-top: none;
        }

        .section {
            margin-bottom: 35px;
        }

        .section-title {
            color: #0066cc;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e9ecef;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .required {
            color: #dc3545;
        }

        input[type="text"], input[type="number"], select, textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            border: 2px solid #e1e8ed;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-family: inherit;
            transition: border-color 0.3s;
            background: #fafbfc;
        }

        input:focus, select:focus, textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #0066cc;
            background: white;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.1);
        }

        textarea {
            resize: vertical;
            min-height: 80px;
        }

        .form-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .submit-section {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .submit-btn {
            background: #0066cc;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
            min-width: 200px;
        }

        .submit-btn:hover {
            background: #004499;
        }

        .privacy-note {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 15px;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .ai-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8f5e8, #f0f8f0);
            border: 1px solid #c3e6c3;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .ai-title {
            color: #2e7d32;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .ai-description {
            color: #1b5e20;
            font-size: 13px;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .form-row {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .container {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
            
            .form-header, .survey-form {
                padding: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="header-content">
            <div class="logo-section">
                <div class="kp-logo">KP</div>
                <div class="mychart-title">MyChart</div>
            </div>
            <div class="patient-info">
                <div style="font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;">Sarah Johnson</div>
                <div style="font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.9;">Pre-Visit Intake</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="breadcrumb">
        <div class="breadcrumb-content">
            <a href="/portal">MyChart Home</a> > <span>Pre-Visit Intake Form</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="form-header">
            <h1 class="form-title">Pre-Visit Intake Form</h1>
            <p class="form-subtitle">
                Please complete this enhanced intake form before your appointment. Your responses help your healthcare provider 
                prepare for a more personalized and efficient visit.
            </p>
            <div class="epic-badge">
                ü§ñ <strong>AI-Enhanced</strong> ‚Ä¢ Powered by EPIC MyChart
            </div>
        </div>

        <form action="/submit-survey" method="POST" class="survey-form">
            <div class="section">
                <h2 class="section-title">
                    üè• Reason for Today's Visit
                </h2>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="primaryReason">What is the primary reason for your visit today? <span class="required">*</span></label>
                    <textarea name="primaryReason" id="primaryReason" required 
                            placeholder="Please describe the main concern or reason for your appointment..."></textarea>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="symptoms">Current symptoms or concerns</label>
                    <textarea name="symptoms" id="symptoms" 
                            placeholder="Describe any symptoms, when they started, and how they affect you..."></textarea>
                </div>

                <div class="form-row">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="painLevel">Current pain level (0-10 scale)</label>
                        <select name="painLevel" id="painLevel">
                            <option value="0">0 - No pain</option>
                            <option value="1">1 - Minimal</option>
                            <option value="2">2 - Mild</option>
                            <option value="3">3 - Uncomfortable</option>
                            <option value="4">4 - Moderate</option>
                            <option value="5">5 - Distracting</option>
                            <option value="6">6 - Distressing</option>
                            <option value="7">7 - Unmanageable</option>
                            <option value="8">8 - Intense</option>
                            <option value="9">9 - Severe</option>
                            <option value="10">10 - Unable to move</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="pronouns">Preferred pronouns</label>
                        <select name="pronouns" id="pronouns">
                            <option value="">Select pronouns</option>
                            <option value="she/her">She/Her</option>
                            <option value="he/him">He/Him</option>
                            <option value="they/them">They/Them</option>
                            <option value="other">Other</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h2 class="section-title">
                    üíä Current Health Status
                </h2>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="medications">Current medications, treatments, or home remedies you've tried</label>
                    <textarea name="medications" id="medications" 
                            placeholder="Include prescription medications, over-the-counter drugs, vitamins, supplements, and any home remedies..."></textarea>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="healthChanges">Recent health changes or allergies</label>
                    <textarea name="healthChanges" id="healthChanges" 
                            placeholder="New symptoms, changes in existing conditions, allergies, hospitalizations, etc..."></textarea>
                </div>

                <div class="form-row">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="sleep">Sleep quality</label>
                        <select name="sleep" id="sleep">
                            <option value="excellent">Excellent (7-9 hours, restful)</option>
                            <option value="good">Good (Generally well-rested)</option>
                            <option value="fair">Fair (Some difficulty sleeping)</option>
                            <option value="poor">Poor (Frequent sleep problems)</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="exercise">Physical activity level</label>
                        <select name="exercise" id="exercise">
                            <option value="daily">Daily exercise</option>
                            <option value="several-times-week">Several times per week</option>
                            <option value="weekly">Weekly</option>
                            <option value="monthly">Monthly</option>
                            <option value="rarely">Rarely</option>
                            <option value="never">Never</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="stress">Current stress level (0-10 scale)</label>
                    <select name="stress" id="stress">
                        <option value="0">0 - No stress</option>
                        <option value="1">1 - Minimal stress</option>
                        <option value="2">2 - Mild stress</option>
                        <option value="3">3 - Moderate stress</option>
                        <option value="4">4 - Noticeable stress</option>
                        <option value="5">5 - Significant stress</option>
                        <option value="6">6 - High stress</option>
                        <option value="7">7 - Very high stress</option>
                        <option value="8">8 - Severe stress</option>
                        <option value="9">9 - Overwhelming stress</option>
                        <option value="10">10 - Extremely stressed</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="section">
                <h2 class="section-title">
                    üòä Personal Connection
                </h2>

                <div class="ai-section">
                    <div class="ai-title">
                        ü§ñ AI-Enhanced Patient Care
                    </div>
                    <div class="ai-description">
                        These personal questions help our AI create a "Quick Connect" summary for your provider, 
                        allowing them to build rapport and provide more personalized care during your visit.
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-row">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="favoriteMovie">Favorite movie or TV show</label>
                        <input type="text" name="favoriteMovie" id="favoriteMovie" 
                               placeholder="This helps your doctor connect with you personally">
                    </div>

                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="additionalComments">Anything else you'd like your provider to know?</label>
                        <textarea name="additionalComments" id="additionalComments" 
                                placeholder="Goals, concerns, questions, or other information..."></textarea>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="funFact">Share something interesting about yourself</label>
                    <textarea name="funFact" id="funFact" 
                            placeholder="A hobby, achievement, current life event, or something unique that might help your doctor remember and connect with you..."></textarea>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="submit-section">
                <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Submit Pre-Visit Intake</button>
                <div class="privacy-note">
                    üîí Your information is secure and will only be shared with your care team at Kaiser Permanente South Bay.<br>
                    This form is processed through EPIC MyChart and may be enhanced with AI to improve your care experience.
                </div>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
